sources.description:
Man... Beast... Or Alien?
In a little Western town, a boy is subjected to rays from a meteor. As a result, he grows into a hairy, psychopathic killer. His mother hides & locks him in her house.

Original title : Teenage Monster (1957)  AKA: Meteor Monster / Meteor Man

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/EyeIyg_4E_4

Director:Jacques R. Marquette
Writer: Ray Buffum
Cast: Anne Gwynne, Stuart Wade, Gloria Castillo, Gil Perkins
Genres:  B movie, Cult Film, Horror, Sci-Fi, Western
